data.description: Don't miss out on this waterfront gem! Priced to move, this 4bed, 2bath home features hardwood floors, open floor plan, and a deck with stunning views.  Vaulted ceilings, gas fireplace, and media room add luxury. Enjoy a cross breeze with screened windows and doors. Additional perks include a gas range, low utilities, no flood insurance required, and no city taxes. This 4-season oasis offers comfort and savings, with public water, fiberoptic high-speed internet, and quick amenities access. Motivated seller!
